title: First Day in CS
author: Oniii_Chan
pages:
#- Anonymous 03/08/20
>first day of spring at my university
>snow has melted, birds are chirping, and I can finally shed my winter jacket
>head to computer science, first class of the day
>kind of running late, so I sprint across campus to make it in time 
#- >by the time I get there I have a bit of sweat built up
>sit in my seat right during attendance
>I look around and realize that I'm the only male in the entire class
>everyone else is a boymoder
#- >they all look kind of uncomfortable
>it's clearly too hot to wear oversized hoodies, so they are all wearing loose tshirts instead
>boymoders without their hoodies are like turtles without their shells
#- >it leave them vulnerable and exposed
>plus you can see their little tits poking through their shirts
>however they seem to be panting, breathing heavilly, stuck in a daze
>suddenly one sticks their nose in the air, and sniffs like a dog
#- >"b-b-boys-s-smell!!"
She moans
>A few other boymoders join her, their bodies slowly turning to look back at me
>Sudden realization hits me
>I sniff myself and sure enough I have a bit of musk from earlier
#- >Oh shit.jpg
>the first one lunges at me without warning but I manage to dodge her
>another goes for my legs, but I slip out of her grasp easilly
>(boymoders have notoriously weak wrists)
#- >I head for the door but a couple of boymoders manage to grab my shirt and tear pieces off it
>like rabid animals they descend on the fabric, trying to inhale it like every sniff would be their last breath
#- >I run out into the hallway, but a swarm of boymoders is out there to see me
>they must have detected my boysmell from the other rooms
>the entire CISC department is overrun with boymoders
#- >see a dude from the other class covered in boymoders, sniffing and kissing every part of his body
>He looks at me, "h-help me..." he pleads
>there's no saving him
>I make it out into the street and it is complete caos
#- >boymoders are in heat
>and the boymoder apocalypse has just begun
#- 